The 2020 Basque regional election was held on Sunday , 12 July 2020 , to elect the 12th Parliament of the Basque Autonomous Community .

Six days later , on 10 February , Urkullu confirmed the election for 5 April , seeking to distance himself from the convoluted political landscape in Catalonia after a 2020 election in the region was announced by Catalan president Quim Torra .
The announcement of the Basque election prompted Galician president Alberto Núñez Feijóo to trigger a snap election in Galicia as well .
